# Checkout v1.0 — CANONICAL FREEZE

**STATUS: CANONICAL | FROZEN | SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH**

Frozen constant: `CHECKOUT_CANONICAL_FROZEN = true` (`lib/checkout/freeze.ts`)  
DOM: `data-checkout-freeze="FROZEN"` · `data-checkout-version="v1.0"`

## Immutable

- Routes under `/checkout/[listingSlug]` (+ address / payment / review / success)
- Buy Now → listing checkout (no cart intermediate for purchase)
- Shell: `CheckoutWizardV1` + `checkout-v1.css` tokens (430px, 64px header, 56px CTA)
- Wallet payment methods SSOT — do not duplicate card management in Checkout
- Sendcloud-only live shipping via Shipping Engine
- Buyer-visible Platform Fee; never expose platform fee as a seller wallet line

## Allowed

- Bug fixes (payment failures, inventory unlock, webhook mapping, a11y, image safety via `SafeImage`)
- Backend/API fixes that do not change frozen layout or copy structure

## Prohibited

- Redesign, layout changes, new Checkout UI surfaces under v1.0
- Reintroducing Parcel2Go / Shippo / parallel checkout providers
- Duplicating payment management outside Wallet
- Structural changes after freeze — ship as **Checkout v1.1**

